  <brief_title>An Observational Study on The Correlation Between Time of Initiation of Avastin (Bevacizumab) Treatment And Progression-Free Survival in Patients With Metastatic Breast Cancer (CRONOS 2)</brief_title>
  <official_title>The Correlation Between the Moment of Bevacizumab theRapy initiatiOn and the Efficacy in patieNt With Metastatic Breast Cancer Treated With First Line Regimens Based On AvaStin</official_title>
  <sponsors>
